# Client Admin Dashboard — Phase 1 Implementation Plan

## Background

The project is a **Next.js 16** app with TailwindCSS, shadcn/ui, next-intl (en/ar), React Query, Axios, React Hook Form, Zod, and MSW. Currently, only the **Auth** feature is built (login/logout/getMe), with a placeholder dashboard page. We need to build the **6 core features** from the PRD.

---

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **API Endpoints**: The PRD doesn't specify exact backend API endpoint paths. The plan assumes RESTful conventions (e.g., `POST /users`, `GET /users/search`, `POST /enrollments`, etc.). Please confirm or provide the actual middleware API spec if available.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Dropdown data for Language / Level / Vehicle**: The PRD mentions these as dropdowns. Are the options static (hardcoded) or fetched from the backend? I'll assume **static options for now** and can switch to API-fetched later.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Scope for today**: This is a large PRD. I recommend we **prioritize and scope what to build today**. My suggestion is below — please confirm or adjust.

### Recommended Priority for Today

| Priority | Feature | Rationale |
|----------|---------|-----------|
| 🥇 1 | Dashboard Layout & Navigation | Foundation for everything else |
| 🥇 2 | Send Single User (form) | Core feature, exercises the full stack |
| 🥈 3 | Send Bulk Users (CSV Upload) | Second most impactful feature |
| 🥉 4 | Enrollment Management (search + CRUD) | Complex but critical |
| 4 | Update User Profile | Relatively simple after enrollment search is built |
| 5 | View Attendance | Read-only, simplest feature |

---

