### Dashboard Layout & Navigation

#### [NEW] [layout.tsx](file:///home/hafez/aanaab/ai-first/src/app/[locale]/dashboard/layout.tsx)

Dashboard shell layout with sidebar navigation containing links to:
- **Add User** (`/dashboard/users/add`)
- **Bulk Import** (`/dashboard/users/bulk`)
- **Manage Enrollments** (`/dashboard/enrollments`)
- **Attendance** (`/dashboard/attendance`)

Uses a clean admin layout with a collapsible sidebar and header with user name + logout + language switcher.

#### [MODIFY] [page.tsx](file:///home/hafez/aanaab/ai-first/src/app/[locale]/dashboard/page.tsx)

Simplify to show a quick-action landing (cards linking to core features).

#### New shadcn/ui components needed

Will add these via shadcn CLI or manual copy:
- **Card** — for dashboard landing cards
- **Select** — for form dropdowns (Language, Level, Vehicle)
- **Dialog** — for confirmation modals (delete enrollment)
- **Alert** — for success/error notifications
- **Textarea** — possibly for notes
- **Badge** — for status indicators
- **Separator** — for layout
- **Sheet** — for mobile sidebar
- **Tabs** — for enrollment management

