### MSW Mock Handlers

#### [MODIFY] [handlers.ts](file:///home/hafez/aanaab/ai-first/src/mocks/handlers.ts)

Add mock handlers for all new endpoints:
- `POST /users` — create single user
- `POST /users/bulk` — bulk upload
- `GET /users/search?q=` — search users
- `PUT /users/:id` — update user profile
- `POST /enrollments` — create enrollment
- `DELETE /enrollments/:id` — delete enrollment
- `POST /enrollments/replace` — replace enrollment
- `GET /attendance` — get attendance records

